  "title": "Plant-parasitic nematodes associated with groundnut in parts of Benin, Burkina Faso, and Nigeria",
  "abstract": "Results are given of survey trips to 6 groundnut producing areas in Benin, 5 in Burkina Faso and 3 in Nigeria in August and September 1989. A list of some important plant parasitic nematode species found associated with groundnut is given. Meloidogyne spp. was not found",
